(44473, 139485, 4096, 2, 'Keep Dreaming', '', '2012-03-11 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 1, 10, '[Keep dreaming]\r\nBy Jayko\r\n\r\nWe''re at the end of the line\r\n(我們還在隊伍的最末端)\r\n\r\nAnd take nothing for sure \r\n(不能確定任何事)\r\n\r\nPumping our heart out and swallowed it down\r\n(心臟都跳出來了再把它吞回去)\r\n\r\nYou are just too far away\r\n(你離我們還很遠)\r\n\r\nDon''t even know our name\r\n(連我們的名字都沒聽過)\r\n\r\nWe are still so far away\r\n(我們還離得很遠)\r\n\r\nWill there be our turn or not\r\n(會不會輪到我們)\r\n\r\n\r\n(We are still so far away)\r\n(我們還離得很遠)\r\n\r\n(We''ll meet you anyway)\r\n(我們總是會見到你的)\r\n\r\n\r\nNo matter how long the queue extended\r\n(不管等待的隊伍排得多長)\r\n\r\nNo matter how long will it takes\r\n(不管要等多久)\r\n\r\nWe know you''ll be there\r\n(我們知道你會在那裡)\r\n\r\nAnd shining as always\r\n(像平常一樣散發著光芒)\r\n\r\nSo we will keep on dreaming\r\n(所以我們會繼續做夢的)\r\n\r\n\r\nCan''t even see the light\r\n(甚至連燈光都看不見)\r\n\r\nCan''t even hear the music\r\n(甚至連音樂都聽不到)\r\n\r\nPumping our heart out and swallowed it down\r\n(心臟都跳出來了再把它吞回去)\r\n\r\nYou are just too far away\r\n(你離我們還很遠)\r\n\r\nDon''t even know our name\r\n(連我們的名字都沒聽過)\r\n\r\nWe are still so far away\r\n(我們還離得很遠)\r\n\r\nWill there be our turn or not \r\n(會不會輪到我們)\r\n\r\n\r\nWe are still so far away\r\n(我們還離得很遠)\r\n\r\nWe''ll meet you anyway\r\n(我們總是會見到你的)\r\n\r\n\r\nNo matter how long the queue extended\r\n(不管等待的隊伍排得多長)\r\n\r\nNo matter how long will it takes\r\n(不管要等多久)\r\n\r\nWe know you''ll be there\r\n(我們知道你會站在那裡)\r\n\r\nAnd smiling as always\r\n(一如平常的笑著)\r\n\r\nSo we will keep on dreaming\r\n(所以我們會繼續做夢的)\r\n\r\n\r\nに歌うよ\r\n (Kimi ni utau yo)\r\n (我為了你而唱）\r\n \r\n君の歌\r\n (kimi no uta)\r\n (你的歌）\r\n \r\n実際はどうの感じてるのかい？\r\n (Jissai wa dō kanji teru no ka)\r\n (你實際聽起來的感受是如何呢？）\r\n \r\n未完成の事は\r\n （MI KAN SEI NO KO TO WA)\r\n (還沒完成的事）\r\n \r\n一つだけ\r\n (HI TO TSU DA KE)\r\n （只剩下一件了）\r\n\r\n\r\nSo let''s keep dreaming\r\n(所以讓我們繼續做夢)\r\n\r\n\r\nNo matter how long the queue extended\r\n(不管等待的隊伍排得多長)\r\n\r\nNo matter how long will it takes\r\n(不管要等多久)\r\n\r\nWe know you''ll be there\r\n(我們知道你會在那裡)\r\n\r\nand shining as always\r\n(像平常一樣散發著光芒)\r\n\r\nSo we will keep dreaming\r\n(所以我們會繼續做夢的)\r\n', '', 239, '', 'Cubic', 'Jayko', 'ChicKNUP', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2012-03-11 23:16:21', '2013-10-07 17:20:34', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
